{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/Description_Banner_Survive.png?t=1739551232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Condemned to purge your death sentence, you and a group of fellow inmates are sent to Earth\u2014a cursed, abandoned wasteland. Teleport to a location of your choice, scavenge for tools, and outlast the competition to earn your freedom. Manage your oxygen carefully, use every resource at your disposal, and, above all, avoid the curse that haunts the planet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/Forecursed_Gif_Teleporter.gif?t=1739551232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/Description_Banner_Curse.png?t=1739551232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Marked by the curse, your mission is clear: pass it on before it consumes your soul. As the hunter, you must target one of your fellow inmates. Deceive them with lies, lure them into traps, or pursue them in a relentless chase. The curse grants you supernatural powers\u2014soar through the air with powerful leaps, track others through walls, and hear their pounding heartbeats. But beware: the longer you remain cursed, the closer you edge toward oblivion.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/Forecursed_Gif_Curse.gif?t=1739551232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053850/extras/Description_Banner_Ghouls.png?t=1739551232\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Death is only the beginning. Consumed by the curse, your soul transforms into one of many ghastly ghouls, each designed to haunt the living. Crawl, 